---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";

const lastUpdated = "2026-06-27";
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy | OSCEN" description="How OSCEN collects, uses, and protects your information across oscen.ai.">
  <Nav />

  <main class="pt-32 pb-24">
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 mb-12">
      <p class="reveal text-[10px] font-mono text-text-muted uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="reveal font-display text-[clamp(2.5rem,6vw,4.5rem)] text-text-primary leading-[0.9]">
        Privacy<br />
        <span class="italic gradient-text">policy.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="reveal text-text-secondary mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Plain English version of how we handle the data you share with us, and what we collect when you use oscen.ai.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-6">
      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">Who we are</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          OSCEN is a neuromorphic AI company building a continuously-learning brain for robotics. The marketing site at oscen.ai is operated by Rio Bold LLC. Reach us at <a href="mailto:info@oscen.ai" class="text-accent-blue hover:underline">info@oscen.ai</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">What we collect</h2>
        <ul class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed space-y-3 list-disc pl-5">
          <li><strong class="text-text-primary">Automatically:</strong> IP address, browser type, pages you visit, and timestamps. Used to operate and secure the site.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text-primary">Through cookies and similar technologies:</strong>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-2">
              <li><strong class="text-text-primary">Essential (always on):</strong> a small consent cookie that remembers your choice, and a session-scoped attribution cookie that captures the UTM tags from links you arrive on.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-text-primary">Analytics (always on, privacy-safe):</strong> Plausible Analytics. It does not use cookies and does not identify you personally.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-text-primary">Advertising (consent required):</strong> Meta Pixel and Google Tag Manager. These set cookies that let Meta and Google's tag partners measure ad performance and let us show relevant ads on Instagram, Facebook, and other Meta properties.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li><strong class="text-text-primary">When you fill out a form:</strong> name, email, and whatever else the form asks. Forms route through Formspree and Buttondown for delivery and newsletter management. Investor inquiries also ask about accreditation status and check size.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">Why we collect it</h2>
        <ul class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>To respond to your inquiry.</li>
          <li>To deliver the newsletter you signed up for.</li>
          <li>To understand which marketing channels are working.</li>
          <li>To show our paid ads to people who are likely to be interested.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mt-3">
          Our paid ad targeting is currently US-only. The site itself is accessible globally and we welcome international visitors. If you fill out a form (for example, as a qualified investor abroad), we process your information under the same standards described here.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">Who we share it with</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-3">We use these processors:</p>
        <ul class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed space-y-1 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Formspree (form delivery)</li>
          <li>Buttondown (newsletter)</li>
          <li>Plausible (analytics)</li>
          <li>Meta (Facebook and Instagram pixel + Conversions API)</li>
          <li>Google (Tag Manager and any tags configured through it)</li>
          <li>Netlify (site hosting)</li>
          <li>Stripe (when applicable for support tier payments)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mt-3">We do not sell your personal information.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">Your rights</h2>
        <ul class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Withdraw consent at any time. Use the <button data-consent-reopen class="text-accent-blue hover:underline">Cookie preferences</button> link to reopen the banner.</li>
          <li>Request a copy of your data.</li>
          <li>Request deletion.</li>
          <li>Object to processing.</li>
          <li>Lodge a complaint with your local supervisory authority.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mt-3">
          To exercise any of these, email <a href="mailto:info@oscen.ai" class="text-accent-blue hover:underline">info@oscen.ai</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">How long we keep data</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Form submissions: indefinitely unless you ask us to delete. Newsletter subscribers: until you unsubscribe. Cookies: the consent cookie lasts 1 year if granted or 90 days if denied. Advertising cookies follow Meta and Google's own retention policies.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">International transfers</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Data may be processed in the United States and other countries where our processors operate. We rely on Standard Contractual Clauses where required.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">Children</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">The site is not directed at children under 16.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">Changes</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          If we materially change our tracking, we will update this page and reset the consent banner so you can choose again.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal glass rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-display text-text-primary mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Questions or requests: <a href="mailto:info@oscen.ai" class="text-accent-blue hover:underline">info@oscen.ai</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm pt-4">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <p class="pt-2">
        <a href="/" class="text-accent-blue hover:underline">&larr; Back to home</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
